@startuml
title UC14 — Admin manages payment plans — State Diagram
[*] --> Idle
Idle --> InProgress : submit payment plan form
InProgress --> Validating : submit/request
Validating --> Completed : success
Validating --> Error : validation/integration/access error
Error --> InProgress : retry/fix input
Completed --> [*]
state Completed {
  [*] --> ResultVisible
  ResultVisible --> Saved : PaymentPlan updated/read
  Saved --> [*]
}
@enduml
